{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"70b060efc1","title":"给林彪周恩来、中央及文革的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2ef81d95c5","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":17,"articleId":"70b060efc1","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0f37ca246a","type":"title","text":"给林彪周恩来、中央及文革的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"70b060efc1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0fdeb3fdb3","type":"paragraph","text":"林、周、中央及文革各同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"70b060efc1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7c2f9d226","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）绝对权威的提法不妥。从来没有单独的绝对权威，凡权威都是相对的，凡绝对的东西都只存在相对的东西之中，犹如绝对真理是无数相对真理的总和．绝对真理只存在于各个相对真理之中一样。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"70b060efc1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aed7c20c11","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）大树特树的说法也不妥。权威和戚信只能从斗争实践中自然地建立，不能由人工去建立，这样建立的威信必然会垮下来。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"70b060efc1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33747b060d","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）党中央很早就禁止祝寿，应通知全国重申此种禁令。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"70b060efc1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"980712b61e","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）湖南的集会应另择日期。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"70b060efc1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5fcc11ebdb","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）我们不要题字。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"70b060efc1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c2e194bcfa","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）会议名称，可同意湖南建议，用第一方案。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"70b060efc1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6935ea08dd","type":"paragraph","text":"以上各点请在一次会议上讨论通过为盼。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"70b060efc1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"47318ab782","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"70b060efc1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"68ba0e717f","type":"subdate","text":"十二月十七日","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"70b060efc1","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":661,"end":660}}}},"__N_SSG":true}